s. Surprisingly, the semiconducting band\ngap nature of o-ZnSb changes from indirect and narrow to direct and sizable\nwhile going from 3D bulk to 2D ML structure. Further, we estimated the value of\nwork functions for the surfaces of t-ZnSb and o-ZnSb as 4.61 eV and 4.04 eV\nrespectively. Such materials can find the niche applications in next generation\nelectronic devices utilizing 2D hetero-structures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 20 Jun 2021 21:41:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Mar 2022 01:08:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-28"}
