tions. Thus, the\ndiversity in magnetism of undoped V2O5 has its origin in defect number density\nas well as their random distribution led to MEPS. This involves localized spins\nin polarons and their FM clusters on the PM background while, V4+ dimers within\nand across the ladder, inducing AFM interactions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Jun 2021 05:57:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Aug 2022 17:51:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-29"}
