nown factors have\na large influence on the efficiency of both processes. Shock obliquity,\nupstream neutral fraction, or other possibilities need to be explored, while\ncalculations assuming fixed values of the epsilons should be regarded as\nprovisional.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Jun 2021 15:32:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-25"}
